.TH LINGUAEDIT-GUI 1 "February 2026" "LinguaEdit 1.7.0" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
linguaedit-gui \- professional translation editor
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B linguaedit-gui
.RI [ FILE ]...
.SH DESCRIPTION
LinguaEdit is a professional translation editor built with PySide6/Qt6.
It supports 17+ file formats including PO, TS, XLIFF, SDLXLIFF, MQXLIFF,
JSON, YAML, Android XML, ARB, PHP, Java Properties, Apple Strings,
Unity Asset, RESX, Chrome i18n, Godot, and Subtitles (SRT/VTT).
.PP
Features include translation memory (TM), glossary management, AI-powered
review, 15+ linting checks, Zen mode, batch translation, concordance
search, and video subtitle preview.
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
.I FILE
One or more translation files to open.
.SH FILES
.TP
.I ~/.config/LinguaEdit/
Configuration directory.
